title: Brainwashed? A Deal Gone Wrong? Charles Manson
description:
Hi my friends! 
I have always gotten suggestions to pleaseee cover this story and here we are. My brain got turned into mush watching all the interviews and reading all the articles, I still don't even fully understand what the heck was going on! 
Would love to hear your thoughts! Hope you have a great rest of your week and I will being seeing you next Monday, woooot. 

x o
Bailey Sarian
